{
  "stem": "9590.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she said-- she threw down, and we ate a potato a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That went on for a few days, till the Germans retreated completely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The house caught fire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we hear that Schindelova is screaming, fire!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fire!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fire!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we knew we-- we had to get out, because we-- we were afraid that we will be there-- burned there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We emerged in the open world, the battleground between the Russians and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I saw in front of me dead Germans-- our side was still the Germans-- dead Germans, wild, wild soldiers, German soldiers, using the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- they-- they lost their head completely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not organized anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were scattered, one and one, different places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was not an army, but they were trying to fight their battle to the last.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At night, the Russian army marched in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that last episode was also our life was hanging on a-- on a string.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because when she said that the fire-- the-- the house took fire, and we were came out, we were afraid to stay outside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were afraid for both-- for the-- for people that will recognize us and will tell them that those are Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were afraid that the battle was there, the fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided that maybe where the mother Kucherova is, on the other side of the road, maybe it's safer there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So first went Szloma's brother, Froiko and Asia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They crossed the-- they wanted to cross the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They crossed it already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then Szloma, and his mother, and I went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As we were approaching the-- the road, a German soldier stopped us and said, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're prisoners.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What-- who are you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
